    "2016; Gabriel 2020; Berk et al. 2021) foot_46 in areas that range from medical diagnosis (Mykhailov 2021) to art (Dare et al.",
    "In sum, while the computational hardness of moral machine learning may be overcome-or distorted-by practice (using massive amounts of training time and data), this practice raises a host of other complicated issues that deserve attention in their own right."
